- Logical operators:
		- &&, || and !
		

- conditional statements:
		- if statement
		- if-else
			- applications of if-else
					- nested if-else
					- else-if ladder
		- switch-case
		
- conditional loops
		- for: when we know the number iteration, then we can use for loop 
		- while: when we do not know the number iteration, then we can use while loop 
		- do-while: here this loop will do post condition checking.

- break and continue
